wwItemDetails: Bill's Organic Sourdough Multi Fruit is a great source of antioxidants.Bill's certified organic stoneground multifruit sourdough is simply unique. Packed with antioxidant goodness from certified organic sultanas, raisins, figs and apricots, all naturally preserved without sulphites. Sulphites can affect some asthmatics and can be the cause of allergies and sensitivities. A delicious combination of sourdough and fruit - but best of all tastes amazing!At Bill's, we're focused on inspiring healthier living through healthier choices. All of our delicious sourdoughs are made using pure, natural ingredients from certified organic farms, milling our flour in a traditional stoneguard method, and allowing our unique natural starter to slowly ferment over 18 hours. Simple. Certified Organic and no nasties.Why 'Certified' Organic? Because we believe it is absolutely essential when creating our highly nutritious and tasty sourdoughs.
